name: language_html_data_attribute_single_quote
description: |
  Apostrophe terminates a single-quoted HTML attribute value. Escaping only
  double quotes leaves templates that use single-quoted attributes vulnerable
  to context changes.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: ascii
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss"
  - "xss-data"
  - "html-attribute-context"
  - "single-quote"
  - "attribute-escaping"
  - "injection-canary"
---
'
